超八成医务人员近期收入下降，8 大科室竞争激烈：疫情下的医疗春招。
More than eighty percent of medical personnel recently income decline, eight departments of the fierce competition: the medical Spring under the epidemic situation.
丁香园 DXY。
DXY, Lilac Garden.
丁香园                      。
